entries.journal_entry_completion_summary: You have met Guri on Dathomir, she would like you to do a job for her.
entries.journal_entry_description: Someone requests your presence on Dathomir.
entries.task00_comm_message_text: [Guri] I have an important proposition for you. Meet me on Dathomir.
entries.task01_journal_entry_description: Speak with Guri to see what is going on.
